80969bbfe30af670148ae2f13","tid":466140,"uid":69872,"like":5,"dislike":12,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:40:07.000Z","msg":"幾欣賞女仔自己一個睇戲 如果係靚女仲更加欣賞"},{"pid":"5c3792a9debaa006382fe990ea335d35e1e1d0ff","tid":466140,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"一直都鍾意自己一個睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但成日覺得入戲院貴，好耐冇去睇"},{"pid":"2e69074318eb5e39c511d470bdb31526a8537ee8","tid":466140,"uid":36673,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"自己睇最好，靜靜咁睇，靜靜咁睇完、思考，當然有人討論更加好，但同唔岩既人睇好睇既電影係會晒左成件事。完左套戲又討論唔到，又要keep住有concersation，好煩。<br />\n<br />\n另外好憎d人睇戲manner好差，只係當entertainment咁睇，文藝片都要食爆谷屌你老母，又以為細細聲就唔係講緊野；一係就係唔撚係都笑、好大反應，嚴重影響到附近既人；最後碌字個時係未撚完嫁，要傾計就出去計唔好撚係到又要扮識睇又要嘈啦仆街。"},{"pid":"c93897249d599cf80325ef633ddf9db6f48b308f","tid":466140,"uid":21222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"成日想睇平戲但太早無人陪，所以經常自己食早餐睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acf1fff0b6bb161cbca54f4e28e29dea4d38fc0","tid":466140,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:25:35.000Z","msg":"電影節打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66faa8ac399984166ff601a01a9c9ac90e4f432","tid":466140,"uid":140222,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"前排有套電影好想睇，但又好少人會岩睇，最後鼓起勇氣自己去<br />\n其實自己一個睇戲都唔係真係想像中咁孤獨，個感覺幾正<br />\n自從果次之後已經諗住間中搵套電影自己去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b926f20e979871ab091547dd3fafdf368a38ba","tid":466140,"uid":157579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:33:09.000Z","msg":"想睇 冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f85d843ec9aa2eed046420b5f53a9a73029ed1c","tid":466140,"uid":137519,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"